data.description: Looking for a spacious family home in a desirable location? Look no further! This stunning colonial home boasts 5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, providing ample space for your growing family or accommodating guests.Located in the Washington Park section of Edison, New Jersey, this property offers convenience and comfort. With easy access to major highways, schools, shopping centers, and restaurants, you'll have everything you need at your fingertips.As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by a welcoming foyer that leads into the open and airy living space. The natural light floods in through large windows, highlighting the beautiful and spacious living and dining areas.The eat in the kitchen plenty of counter space, storage, and modern appliances. Whip up delicious meals for your loved ones while still being able to interact with them in the adjacent family room.Retreat to your private master suite, complete with two large closets. The additional four bedrooms offer plenty of space. Convenient upper level washer/dryer The main bath boasts skylights, shower and tub Step outside and enjoy your own private oasis in the backyard. Host barbecues on the patio in the private fenced in yard. The possibilities are endless! Great covered carport with side door right into the kitchen Do not miss the 2 Car detached garage that can be used for parties, game day, office use or convert back for vehicle storage.Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this beautiful colonial home yours. Schedule a showing today and come see!!
